   <section class=\"block block--colored block-page-header about about--students\">\n      <h1 class=\"block-page-header__heading heading--students\">Students</h1>\n    </section>\n    <section class=\"block block--light block--instructions--preview about about--student\">\n      <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"block__text\">\n          <header class=\"block__header\">\n            <p>\n              Shiftly connects you with flexible, paid shifts at local\n              restaurants—on your schedule. Whether you're looking to earn extra\n              money between classes or gain real-world experience, Shiftly makes\n              it easy.\n            </p>\n          </header>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n    <section class=\"block block--light block--instructions about about--student\">\n      <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"block__text\">\n          <header class=\"block__header\">\n            <h2 class=\"block__heading\">How it Works:</h2>\n          </header>\n          <div class=\"block__paragraph\">\n            <h3 class=\"block__sub-heading\">1. browse shifts near you</h3>\n            <p>\n              Log in to see a list of available shifts from nearby restaurants.\n              Each post includes:\n            </p>\n            <ul class=\"list\">\n              <li class=\"list__item\">Date and time</li>\n              <li class=\"list__item\">Hourly wage</li>\n              <li class=\"list__item\">Location</li>\n              <li class=\"list__item\">\n                Job description (ex: hosting, dishwashing, cashiering, etc.)\n              </li>\n            </ul>\n            <p>\n              Shifts are updated in real-time, so check back often or turn on\n              notifications for new postings.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"block__paragraph\">\n            <h3 class=\"block__sub-heading\">2. apply first, get the shift</h3>\n            <p>See a shift you like? Tap to apply.</p>\n            <ul class=\"list\">\n              <li class=\"list__item\">\n                Shifts are first-come, first-served–if you're the first to\n                apply, it's yours!\n              </li>\n              <li class=\"list__item\">\n                Restaurants can view your profile and rating, so keeping a good\n                track record helps you not get rejected\n              </li>\n            </ul>\n            <p>\n              You'll get a confirmation with all the shift details once you're\n              approved.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"block__paragraph\">\n            <h3 class=\"block__sub-heading\">3. show up and do great work</h3>\n            <p>On the day of your shift:</p>\n            <ul class=\"list\">\n              <li class=\"list__item\">\n                Be on time, dress appropriately, and be ready to help\n              </li>\n              <li class=\"list__item\">\n                Follow the instructions given in the job description or by the\n                staff\n              </li>\n            </ul>\n            <p>\n              Communicate clearly if anything comes up–restaurants value\n              professionalism!\n            </p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"block__paragraph\">\n            <h3 class=\"block__sub-heading\">\n              4. get rated & rate the restaurant\n            </h3>\n            <p>\n              After your shift, the restaurant will rate your performance based\n              on:\n            </p>\n            <ul class=\"list\">\n              <li class=\"list__item\">\n                Punctuality: did you arrive on time and ready to work?\n              </li>\n              <li class=\"list__item\">\n                Work Ethic: did they complete tasks efficiently and with care?\n              </li>\n              <li class=\"list__item\">\n                Professionalism: were you respectful, positive, and\n                communicative?\n              </li>\n            </ul>\n            <p>You also get to rate the restaurant based on:</p>\n            <ul class=\"list\">\n              <li class=\"list__item\">\n                Clarity of expectations: were the tasks clearly explained?\n              </li>\n              <li class=\"list__item\">\n                Work environment: was the team respectful and the environment\n                safe?\n              </li>\n              <li class=\"list__item\">\n                Overall experience: did you feel supported and treated fairly?\n              </li>\n            </ul>\n            <p>\n              Your average rating builds your Shiftly reputation, which helps\n              you stand out and reduces the chances of being rejected from\n              future shifts. Meanwhile, your feedback helps other students make\n              informed decisions–and encourages restaurants to create great work\n              experiences.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"block__paragraph\">\n            <h3 class=\"block__sub-heading\">5. get paid immediately</h3>\n            <p>\n              Shiftly pays you directly after the restaurant confirms that your\n              shift was completed.\n            </p>\n            <ul class=\"list\">\n              <li class=\"list__item\">\n                Get paid the same day (in most cases—some payments may take 1\n                business day depending on your bank)\n              </li>\n              <li class=\"list__item\">\n                You'll receive a summary of your completed shifts and earnings\n              </li>\n            </ul>\n            <p>\n              Fast, simple, and reliable. Just show up, do great work, and get\n              paid.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n    <section class=\"block block--colored about about--student\">\n      <div class=\"block__text\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n          <div class=\"block__text\">\n            <header class=\"block__header\">\n              <h2>Why Shiftly Benefits Students</h2>\n            </header>\n            <div class=\"block__paragraph\">\n              <ul class=\"list\">\n                <li class=\"list__item\">\n                  Pick up shifts that fit your schedule\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"list__item\">No long-term commitments</li>\n                <li class=\"list__item\">No resumes or interviews</li>\n                <li class=\"list__item\">Get paid right away</li>\n              </ul>\n              <p>\n                Whether you're saving for textbooks or just want to grab dinner\n                with friends, Shiftly helps you earn money and experience–on\n                your terms.\n              </p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"block__penguin\">\n            <img src=\"/253245c6102f71845525e657952ff217.svg\" alt=\"\">\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n    <section class=\"block block--dark block--bottom\">\n      <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"block__text students\">\n          <header class=\"column__header\">\n            <h4 class=\"column_heading\">Students</h4>\n          </header>\n          <div class=\"list\">\n            <a href=\"/a06f72b3e226a32ee6e99456d3af971a.html\">How it Works</a>\n            <a href=\"/b6ae2fbbb3871a11238b1eb15d3a4c5f.html\">FAQs</a>\n            <a href=\"/b6ae2fbbb3871a11238b1eb15d3a4c5f.html\">Tips for Getting Hired</a>\n            <a href=\"/b6ae2fbbb3871a11238b1eb15d3a4c5f.html\">Payment & Earnings</a>\n            <a href=\"/b6ae2fbbb3871a11238b1eb15d3a4c5f.html\">Support</a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"block__text students\">\n          <header class=\"column__header\">\n            <h4 class=\"column_heading\">Businesses</h4>\n          </header>\n          <div class=\